@node Features "OLFB Features"

  *** Features ***

  This is a fully functional FootBall simulation that can
  be played over MANY Amiga BBS systems.

  + This game will run on BBBBS, Cnet, Trinity, DLG, E! 4D and
    TransAmiga systems and supports a "CLI MODE" allowing it
    to run on almost ANY Amiga BBS system!

    After setting it up, the game will determine which system
    is running it and adjust itself accordingly! This is the
    ONLY game (that I know of) that has this feature!

  + User configurable
    BBBBS & DLG --
     Each user can select either ANSI or ASCII graphics in both
     B&W or Color!
    Cnet --
     The users BBS settings will be utilized in the game and can
     be edited while inside the game.
    ALL --
     Users can @{"Challenge the Sysop" link SYSCHAL} to play one on one, live
     online!
     Each user can individually turn ON/OFF game animation at any
     time!
     Each user can individually adjust his text display speed
     depending on his reading speed or modem speed preferences.
     The sysop can adjust the ODDS of a play resulting in a penalty
     from within the versitile Sysop menu.
     Games are automatically saved when a player quits so he can
     play a single game over several sessions.
  + Full featured Stats
     The game will track and sort 9 different stat categories for
     each player and display them on the the OLFB stat Sheet!
  + Easy to Customize
     The plays can be easily @{"customized" link CUSTOMIZE} or added to by the Sysop!

@endnode

