@node TA.full "Complete Installation for TransAmiga"

     Attention!

      There were some errors in the OLFB docs of version 1.6
      regarding TA setup.. This has been fixed! The TA File
      setup is the same as the CLI MODE setup.

      Setup Files according to The @{"CLI MODE" link F.SETUP} and then come back
      here.


==========================================================================

     The following section was provided by Jerry Jordan. Thanks Jerry!

==========================================================================

     1. Edit the file "OLFB.trans" line # 24 to reflect the path of where
        you installed the game.

     2. Copy the file "OLFB.trans" to your games directory.

     3. Add the following to your Extras.Rx file in your Configs directory.

         N OLFB                     5 -------- OLFB.trans

         ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
         Change the above for your needs, but leave the spaces!

     4. Play the game. :)  Hopefully I didn't forget anything!!

     I can be contacted at Hawk's Haven BBS Tel. +354-2-54758,,,,,,,,,,,,1#1
     (12 commas for a Fax/Voice Switch *BOY I NEED A BETTER ANSWER MACHINE*)
     or by mail at:
                      Jerry Jordan
                      PSC 1013 Box 628
                      APO AE 09725-0628
                      USA

     This address is physically in Iceland, but this is a US Air Force mailing
     address in the USA. Matt's address can be found in the @{"Registration.Doc" link REGISTER}

==========================================================================

    Please consider @{"Registering Online FootBall." link REGISTER}

    That's it! If you see any bugs, let me know. (I mean it..)
    Matt (503)761-3043

    Enjoy.

@endnode

